HEADWORD: Prevene
<hw>Pre*vene"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>pr⟦eacute⟧venir</ets>, L. <ets>praevenire</ets>. See
<er>Prevent</er>.]</ety> <def>To come before; to anticipate; hence, to
hinder; to prevent.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Philips.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

